data.description: Step into the warmth of this all brick renovated cape, boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. The heart of this home is the recently updated kitchen featuring new white cabinets that seamlessly blend style, functionality and storage. Laminate countertops provide a sleek and easy-to-maintain surface, while stainless steel appliances add a touch of contemporary elegance. As you explore the home, the gleaming hardwood floors catch your eye, flowing seamlessly throughout. The layout of this cape is both practical and spacious, ensuring comfortable living making it a perfect place to call home.
